{
  "texts": [
    "In this presentation we highlight some of these differences.",
    "Moreover, we find that working across these different contexts also surfaces the importance of collaborators.",
    "Within these spaces we find collaborators in the form of different organizations, and, more importantly, people.",
    "For instance, some of our programs include coaches, professional athletes, and sports technology founders, who serve as facilitators/educators for youth.",
    "These individuals model what it means to design with and utilize AI/ML in the creation of sports wearables."
  ]
}